{"tid":1042591,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[反港獨是毋用置疑] 連登已由港獨份子溫床變成港獨份子人人喊打的愛國論壇","createTime":"2019-03-01T16:05:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-02T18:14:38.000Z","uid":93380,"like":5,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0aa400070cb8218c7cf838ce0150dcf23bf0e40a","tid":1042591,"uid":93380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T16:05:02.000Z","msg":"連登已由港獨份子溫床變成反港獨先峰的愛國論壇<br />\n體現總體國家安全觀<br />\n同志們 做得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望愛國份子繼續堅定支持中央<br />\n對習近平新時代中國特色社會主義思想保持信心<br />\n打擊港獨的有生力量<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20171018/photo/bkncn-20171018101920182-1018_05011_001_01b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171018%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20171018101920182-1018_05011_001_01b.jpg&h=a15b6b88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另附上&lt;习近平新时代中国特色社会主义思想的世界意义&gt;一文<br />\n愛國之士做好思想武裝, 知識武裝<br />\n為實現中華民族偉大復興而努力<br />\n<a href=\"http://theory.people.com.cn/n1/2018/1204/c40531-30441761.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftheory.people.com.cn%2Fn1%2F2018%2F1204%2Fc40531-30441761.html&d=u7xsq8u58TeopDPyjGw7C80oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=f35b25eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://theory.people.com.cn/n1/2018/1204/c40531-30441761.html</a>"},{"pid":"91f942839b59ac54be367a5800c4e95f40b68b27","tid":1042591,"uid":93380,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T16:07:37.000Z","msg":"另外，請大家多多支持林特首，依法施政<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/375/cpsprodpb/13FEE/production/_95320918_hi038694294.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F375%2Fcpsprodpb%2F13FEE%2Fproduction%2F_95320918_hi038694294.jpg&h=db1c9f33&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bcf171a5a65ddb471ae136af32db201094315290","tid":1042591,"uid":19527,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":